{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"Hi. For those of you who haven't seen dancing bears,"},{"time":5000,"text":"these are the dancing bears."},{"time":7000,"text":"In 1995, we started working on a two-year investigative research project"},{"time":10000,"text":"to try and find out what was going on."},{"time":13000,"text":"Because the sloth bears in the wild were obviously getting depleted"},{"time":15000,"text":"because of this."},{"time":17000,"text":"This is the Qalandar community. They are a marginalized Islamic community"},{"time":21000,"text":"who live across India,"},{"time":23000,"text":"and have been in India since the 13th century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"We went about getting evidence of what was going on."},{"time":31000,"text":"And this is footage from a hidden camera in a button."},{"time":33000,"text":"And we went in, pretending to be buyers."},{"time":35000,"text":"And we found this right in this very state, in Karnataka."},{"time":38000,"text":"And the bear cubs were being harvested from across the country"},{"time":41000,"text":"and being sold and traded."},{"time":43000,"text":"These were being sold for about 2,000 dollars each,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and they are used for bear paw soup,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and also being trained, later on,"},{"time":49000,"text":"to become dancing bears like the one you just saw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"Sadly, the family of Qalandars depended on this bear."},{"time":57000,"text":"The couple are barely 18 years old."},{"time":60000,"text":"They already have four children beside them. You can see them."},{"time":63000,"text":"And the economy of the family and their livelihood depended on those animals."},{"time":66000,"text":"So, we had to deal with it in a very practical and sustainable manner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"Now, when we started working deeper and digging deeper,"},{"time":72000,"text":"we found that it's an illegal act."},{"time":74000,"text":"These guys could go to jail for up to seven years"},{"time":77000,"text":"if they were caught by authorities."},{"time":79000,"text":"And what they were doing to the bears was really appalling."},{"time":81000,"text":"It was unacceptable."},{"time":84000,"text":"The mother bears are usually killed."},{"time":86000,"text":"The cubs, which are taken, are separated."},{"time":89000,"text":"Their teeth are basically bashed out with a metal rod."},{"time":92000,"text":"And they use a red hot iron needle to make a hole through the muzzle."},{"time":96000,"text":"Now we had to start changing these people and converting them from using that"},{"time":100000,"text":"for a livelihood, to getting something else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"So, this is Bitu Qalandar, who was our first experiment."},{"time":105000,"text":"And we were so unsure that this would work."},{"time":107000,"text":"We weren't sure at all. And we managed to convince him."},{"time":110000,"text":"And we said, \"Okay, here is some seed fund."},{"time":112000,"text":"Let's see if you can get something else.\" And we got the bear surrendered"},{"time":114000,"text":"to -- we set up a sanctuary. We have four sanctuaries in India."},{"time":117000,"text":"And now he sells cool drinks, he's by the highway."},{"time":120000,"text":"He has a telephone booth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"And then it started, there was no turning back after that."},{"time":125000,"text":"This is Sadua who came and surrendered his bear."},{"time":127000,"text":"And now he runs a cattle fodder store and a grain store"},{"time":131000,"text":"near Agra."},{"time":133000,"text":"Then there was no looking back at all for us."},{"time":135000,"text":"We gave cycle rickshaws."},{"time":137000,"text":"We set up carpet-weaving units,"},{"time":139000,"text":"vocational training for the women."},{"time":141000,"text":"The women were just not allowed to come out of the community"},{"time":143000,"text":"and work with mainstream society. So, we were able to address that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Education. The kids never went to school."},{"time":149000,"text":"They only had Islamic education, very little of it."},{"time":151000,"text":"And they were never allowed to go to school"},{"time":153000,"text":"because they were an extra earning hand at home. So we managed to get education."},{"time":156000,"text":"So, we sponsor 600 children education programs today."},{"time":160000,"text":"We were able to ensure brighter futures for these people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Of course we also had to get the bears in."},{"time":165000,"text":"This is what happens to the bears when they come in."},{"time":167000,"text":"And this is what we turn them into."},{"time":169000,"text":"We have a veterinary facility in our rescue centers."},{"time":172000,"text":"So, basically in 2002 there were"},{"time":174000,"text":"1,200 dancing bears."},{"time":176000,"text":"We rescued over 550 dancing bears."},{"time":179000,"text":"We've been able to ensure better futures for the people and the bears."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"The big news that I want to announce today"},{"time":184000,"text":"is that next month we will be bringing in"},{"time":187000,"text":"the very last bear of India,"},{"time":190000,"text":"into our rescue center."},{"time":192000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":196000,"text":"And India will no longer have to witness this cruel barbaric practice"},{"time":200000,"text":"which has been here for centuries."},{"time":202000,"text":"And the people can hold their heads up high."},{"time":204000,"text":"And the Qalandar people will rise above all this cruel barbaric past"},{"time":207000,"text":"that they've lived all their lives."},{"time":209000,"text":"And the beautiful bears can of course live in the wild again."},{"time":212000,"text":"And there will be no more removing of these bears."},{"time":215000,"text":"And the children, both humans and bear cubs"},{"time":218000,"text":"can live peacefully. Thank you."},{"time":220000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}